  <h2>Trust Tiers</h2>

  <p>Skillsmith categorizes skills by trust level to help you make informed decisions:</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Tier</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>official</code></td>
        <td>Anthropic or partner skills with full security review</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>verified</code></td>
        <td>Publisher verified, quality checked</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>community</code></td>
